pool_system.pool_manager -> pool_system.descriptors: manages
pool_system.pool_manager -> pool_system.chunk_manager: coordinates
pool_system.pool_manager -> pool_system.freelist_manager: coordinates

pool_system.chunk_manager -> pool_system.chunks: maintains
pool_system.freelist_manager -> pool_system.freelists: maintains

pool_system.descriptors.descriptor1 -> pool_system.chunks.chunk_list1: references
pool_system.descriptors.descriptor2 -> pool_system.chunks.chunk_list2: references

pool_system.chunks.chunk_list1 -> pool_system.freelists.free_list1: provides blocks
pool_system.chunks.chunk_list2 -> pool_system.freelists.free_list2: provides blocks